title: Ep 2268 - Where Is The Flag?
shortDesc: Jethalal is unable to control his excitement to hoist the flag. All the residents assemble for the flag hoisting ceremony. Bhide asks Iyer to get the flag. However, Iyer realises that he has left the bag containing the flag in an auto.

title: Ep 2269 - Jethalal And Iyer Have An Argument
shortDesc: When Jethalal finds out that Iyer has misplaced the bag, he accuses him of being jealous and intentionally losing the bag to embarrass him in front of his guests.

title: Ep 2270 - Surprise Guest At Gokuldham
shortDesc: The residents are shocked when they learn that the celebrations are cancelled. But they are in for a surprise when an autorickshaw driver comes and gives them the flag that Iyer had misplaced.

title: Ep 2271 - Tappu Senas Janmashtami Celebrations
shortDesc: Tappu Sena ask the residents of Gokuldham Society to assemble for the Janmashtami celebrations. The residents are entertained to folk music. Later, Abdul comes and announces that there is a huge surprise lined up for them.

title: Ep 2272 - The Rs 51,000 Bill
shortDesc: Gokuldham residents are extremely elated after Tappu Sena organises a Dahi Handi in the society premises. The next day, Atmaram Bhide gets a bill from the event planner. He is shocked when sees that the bill is a massive 51,000 rupees.

title: Ep 2273 - Gokuldhams Ganapati Darshan
shortDesc: Bhide questions Tappu on overspending for the Janmashtami celebrations. However, when Tappu tells him that he has arranged for sponsors, Bhide is happy. Later, the residents of Gokuldham offer prayers at a Ganesh temple in Pune.

title: Ep 2274 - Food For Thought
shortDesc: Jethalal is surprised to see Babita at the balcony after a long time. When she asks him about a coconut based sweet, he immediately offers to get it for her. Meanwhile, Atmaram Bhide allows Hathi to write the 'Thought For The Day'.

title: Ep 2275 - Komals Outfit Woes
shortDesc: Hansraj Hathi receives an invite to attend a special programme for doctors. Excited, he asks Komal to shop for a good outfit so that they could win the prize for 'Best Couple'. Komal visits several outlets but is unable to find her perfect dress.

title: Ep 2276 - Weight Issues
shortDesc: Komal is dejected when she is unable to find a suitable dress due to her weight. She gets determined to lose weight and enrolls herself in a weight-loss programme. Will she be able to purchase the western outfit and help Hansraj Hathi win the prize

title: Ep 2277 - Komals Laugh Riot
shortDesc: Komal meets a dietitian, who misguides her and asks her not to reveal about her new diet to anyone. She also teaches a new way to stay healthy, by laughing out loud for no reason, to Komal.

title: Ep 2278 - The Incorrect Weighing Machine
shortDesc: Hansraj asks Jethalal to get him a weighing machine. Jethalal instructs Bagha to get a new machine. But, he ends up purchasing an incorrect machine. Meanwhile, when Babita gets rabdi for everyone, Komal is tempted to eat.

title: Ep 2279 - The Football Match
shortDesc: Komal is desperate to lose weight and decides to engage in some sporting activities. She joins Tappu Sena for a game of football. Bhide, Madhvi, Iyer and Babita are astonished when they see Komal playing with the boys.

title: Ep 2280 - Komals Secret Mission
shortDesc: Komal's efforts to lose weight takes a wrong turn when she tries to keep her efforts a secret. She doesn't want anyone else to know about her intention and even then she must lose weight.

title: Ep 2281 - Sonus Gift For Komal Bhabhi
shortDesc: Komal overexerts herself in a bid to lose weight and fit into the western dress and faints at the park. Komal is forced to reveal about her weight loss plan when the residents ask her. Sonu decides to design a new western outfit for Komal.

title: Ep 2282 - Komal And Hathi Win A Prize
shortDesc: Komal and Hansraj Hathi attend the party organised for doctors and participate in an array of activities. They are jubilant when the host gives them an award for being the 'Best Couple'. They share their happiness with Gokuldham residents.
